OL,3,CPride of Britain: Meet Regional
OL,4,CFundraiser of the Year Finalist Emma
OL,5,CCurrie
OL,7,FIt is that time of year again where we
OL,8,Fcelebrate those from our communities
OL,9,Fwho have given their time to raise
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds to help others.
OL,12,FWe've been searching for the ITV
OL,13,FBorder Pride of Britain Regional
OL,14,FFundraiser of the Year, and have
OL,15,Fwhittled it down to four outstanding
OL,16,Ffinalists.
OL,18,FEmma Currie, from Dumfries, has taken
OL,19,Fit upon herself to ensure that every
OL,20,Fprimary school in the town has a
OL,21,Fdefibrillator.
