OL,4,CFundraiser of the Year Finalist Emma
OL,5,CCurrie
OL,7,FShe was inspired by the death of Emma
OL,8,FRoss who died when she suffered a
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest in her school
OL,10,Fplayground in 2014. She died three
OL,11,Fyears later as a result.
OL,13,FEmma Currie said: "When I started this
OL,14,Fjob in 2016 wee Emma's story stuck
OL,15,Fwith me in the fact that she had a
OL,16,Fcardiac arrest on her school
OL,17,Fplayground.
