OL,3,CPride of Britain: Meet Regional
OL,4,CFundraiser of the Year Finalist Emma
OL,5,CCurrie
OL,7,F"It was just something that I felt
OL,8,Fhaving a defibrillator at school was
OL,9,Fobviously super important to have. I
OL,10,Fhad just assumed that everybody would
OL,11,Ffollow suit with a defibrillator.
OL,13,F"And after what happened to wee Emma,
OL,14,Fafter a few phone calls, it became
OL,15,Fclear in the schools that wasn't the
OL,16,Fcase.
