OL,3,CPride of Britain: Meet Regional
OL,4,CFundraiser of the Year Finalist Emma
OL,5,CCurrie
OL,7,F"It was just something I felt really
OL,8,Fstrongly the school should have and
OL,9,Fit's something that needed to be done.
OL,10,FSo that was the start of Wee Emma's
OL,11,Fcampaign.
OL,13,F"If something needs doing, then just
OL,14,Fdo it. It was just something that
OL,15,Fneeded done."
OL,17,FEmma then launched her campaign and
OL,18,Faimed to gather enough money to ensure
OL,19,Fevery primary school in Dumfries has a
OL,20,Fdefibrillator.
