OL,7,FShe thought it would take her three
OL,8,Fyears to complete but in reality it
OL,9,Fonly took her less than a month.
OL,11,FIn total Emma raised more than thirty-
OL,12,Fthree thousand pounds and ensured that
OL,13,Fteachers and pupils were trained to
OL,14,Fuse the life-saving equipment.
